    <h1 class="article-title">Nothing New Under the Sun</h1>
    <p class="article-subtitle">AI, Sense Perception, and the God Who Grounds All Knowing</p>
    <div class="article-meta">
      <span>The Kiln Ministries</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Drawn from Herman Bavinck · Ecclesiastes · Romans</span>
    </div>

    <div class="download-callout">
      <p>
        <strong>Full Essay Available as PDF</strong>
        The complete version — with full theological argument, epistemological diagram, and implications for soul care — is available as a free PDF.
      </p>
      <a href="/library/nothing-new-under-the-sun.pdf" class="btn-download" download>
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M8 1v9M8 10l-3-3M8 10l3-3M2 13h12" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        Download PDF
