      <p><strong>Sources:</strong> Holy Scripture (ESV); John Calvin, <em>Institutes of the Christian Religion</em>; Herman Bavinck, <em>Reformed Dogmatics</em> Vol. 2, <em>Christian Worldview</em>, <em>Philosophy of Revelation</em>; Thomas Watson, <em>A Body of Divinity</em>; Thomas Boston, <em>Human Nature in Its Fourfold State</em>; Richard Sibbes, <em>The Bruised Reed</em>; John Owen, selected works.</p>
