    <h1 class="article-title">The Wound at the Root</h1>
    <p class="article-subtitle">Sin and the Fractured Self — The Fall, Original Sin, and the Depth of Human Corruption</p>
    <div class="article-meta">
      <span>The Kiln Ministries</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Calvin · Bavinck · Owen · The Puritans</span>
    </div>

    <div class="series-nav">
      <p>What It Means to Be Human — A Three-Part Series</p>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/library/what-it-means-to-be-human-part1.html">Crowned with Glory — The Image of God in Man</a></li>
        <li class="current">The Wound at the Root — Sin and the Fractured Self</li>
        <li>Renewed After the Image — Redemption and the Restored Person <em style="color: var(--color-muted);">(coming soon)</em></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

